[center][b][u]Multi Pking[/u][/b][/center]
Search for 

[code]public boolean multiCombat() {[/code]

You should get something that looks like this
[code]public boolean multiCombat() {
	if((absX >= 3144 && absX <= 3184 && absY >= 3519 && absY <=3656) || (absX >= 3185 && absX <= 3350 && absY >= 3502 && absY <=3900) || (absX >= 2983 && absX <= 3007 && absY >= 3905 && absY <=3917) || (absX >= 3007 && absX <= 3075 && absY >= 3608 && absY <=3713) || (absX >= 2944 && absX <= 2963 && absY >= 3812 && absY <=3827) || (absX >= 3041 && absX <= 3057 && absY >= 3869 && absY <=3883) || (absX >= 3157 && absX <= 3181 && absY >= 3874 && absY <=3895) || (absX >= 2720 && absX <= 2760 && absY >= 5073 && absY <=5114) || (absX >= 2256 && absX <= 2287 && absY >= 4680 && absY <=4711) || (absX >= 2360 && absX <= 2445 && absY >= 5045 && absY <= 5125) || (absX >= 2760 && absX <= 2780 && absY >= 2790 && absY <=2810) || (absX >= 2624 && absX <= 2690 && absY >= 2550 && absY <=2619) || (absX >= 3460 && absX <= 3520 && absY >= 9470 && absY <=9530) || (absX >= 2371 && absX <= 2424 && absY >= 5125 && absY <=5167) || (absX >= 2627 && absX <= 2677 && absY >= 4550 && absY <=4602) || (absX >= 3249 && absX <= 3307 && absY >= 3904 && absY <=3952) || (absX >= 2420 && absX <= 2520 && absY >= 10100 && absY <=10200) || (absX >= 2992 && absX <= 3090 && absY >= 4804 && absY <=4872))
[/code]
Then go into the corners where you want the pk area to be and find your absX and absY and add this into the code
[code](absX >= XXLL && absX <= XXHH && absY >= YYLL && absY <=YYHH) ||[/code]

XXLL means that the absX's last two numbers have to be lower then the XXHH last two numbers and YYLL means your absY's last two numbers has to be lower then the YYHH last two numbers.

If you get an error, then its
[code](absX >= XXHH && absX <= XXLL && absY >= YYHH && absY <=YYLL) ||[/code]

XXHH means that your absX's last two numbers has to be higher then XXLL's last two. And YYHH means your absY's last two numbers has to be higher then YYLL's last two.

Then add this under that, or maybe under other things like any "isin" coordinates.
[code][code]public boolean isInYourPk() {
	if((absX >= XXXX && absX <= XXXX && absY >= YYYY && absY <=YYYY))
	return true;
	else
	return false;
	}
[/code]
Change the XXXX and YYYY to your coordinates.

Now, find
[code]ResetAttack();[/code]

And add above the "break;" add
[code]if(isInYourPk()){
wildyLevel = 130; <---- Change the wilderness level to whatever you like
}[/code]

Now search for (ctrl + F)
[code]public boolean isInWilderness(int coordX[/code]

And you should find this,
[code]	public boolean isInWilderness(int coordX, int coordY, int Type) {
[/code]

Under that put,
[code]	if(isInYourPk()) return true;
[/code]

Then search for,
[code]sM("Other player is busy at the moment.");
break;
}
[/code]

Under that put,
[code]if(isInYourPk())
{
  wildyLevel = 200;<---- Change the wilderness level to whatever you like
}
[/code]

Then search for,
[code]			int level = ((absY - 3520) / 8) + 1;
[/code]

Under that put this,
[code]			if(isInYourPk()){level = 200;}		<---- Change the wilderness level to whatever you like	
[/code]


